  "privacy": {
    "title": "Privacy Policy",
    "lastUpdated": "Last updated: April 1, 2026",
    "s1Title": "1. General",
    "s1Text": "This Privacy Policy describes how the Runwise app collects, uses, and protects your personal data. By using the app, you agree to the terms of this policy.",
    "s2Title": "2. Data We Collect",
    "s2Text": "We receive the following data from your Strava account:",
    "s2Item1": "Workout data: distance, pace, time, heart rate, elevation, GPS tracks",
    "s2Item2": "Basic Strava profile info: name, user ID",
    "s2Item3": "Data you enter manually: age, height, weight, goals, personal records",
    "s2Item4": "App settings: language, AI coach preferences",
    "s2Item5": "Chat history with the AI coach",
    "s3Title": "3. How We Use Data",
    "s3Text": "Your data is used exclusively for:",
    "s3Item1": "Analyzing workouts and generating personal recommendations using AI (DeepSeek)",
    "s3Item2": "Generating personalized training plans",
    "s3Item3": "Displaying statistics, progress, and workout history",
    "s4Title": "4. Third-Party Data Sharing",
    "s4Text": "Workout data may be sent to the DeepSeek AI service solely for generating analysis and recommendations. Data is stored in a Supabase database. We do not sell, share, or disclose your data to any other third parties. Data is not used to train AI models.",
    "s5Title": "5. Data Storage and Security",
    "s5Text": "Data is stored on Supabase servers with encryption. Access to data is restricted and only available through authorized requests. We take reasonable measures to protect your data but cannot guarantee absolute security of data transmission over the internet.",
    "s6Title": "6. Your Rights",
    "s6Text": "You can revoke the app's access to your Strava account at any time through Strava settings. When you log out, local data is deleted from your device. To delete server-side data, you can contact us.",
    "s7Title": "7. Policy Changes",
    "s7Text": "We reserve the right to modify this policy. In case of significant changes, we will notify you through the app."
  },
